Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Functional Safety Market

Functional safety market size is valued at USD 6.46 billion by 2028 is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate of 6.87% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on functional safety provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecasted period while providing their impacts on the marketâ€™s growth.

Functional safety is the type of a safety system for automation protection. Functional safety is appropriate for checking on inputs and breakdown responses to foretell the error in a fail-safe manner.

The strict mandate for safety regulations is expected to influence the growth of functional safety market over the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Also the rapid demand for safety systems in oil and gas industry and the rise in the requirement for reliable safety systems to ensure personnel and asset protection are also anticipated to flourish the growth of the functional safety market. Furthermore, the increase in the industrial revolution 4.0 and financial policy steps taken by regional financial institutions to keep manufacturing facilities floating amid COVID-19 crisis are also likely to positively impact the growth of the market. Moreover, the rise in the awareness and concerns regarding the safety of individuals and the increase in the number of manufacturing industries are also expected create a huge demand for functional safety as well as lifting the growth of the functional safety market.

However, the high investment required for installing functional safety systems and the dearth of awareness and complexity of standards are expected to act as the major limitations for the growth of functional safety in the above mentioned forecasted period, whereas the lack of functional safety certified workforce and the high complexity of safety applications can challenge the functional safety market growth in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

Likewise, the rapid rise in the acceptance of workplace safety standards in emerging economies, rapid technological advancements and increase in the usage of industrial internet of things are expected to create various new opportunities that will lead to the growth of the functional safety market in the above mentioned forecasted period.

